OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FUnpaid carers in Wales are "at
OL,7,Fbreaking point" due to a system that
OL,8,Frepeatedly fails to recognise, support
OL,9,For uphold their basic legal rights,
OL,10,Faccording to a new report.
OL,12,FThe Senedd's Health and Social Care
OL,13,FCommittee's inquiry heard evidence
OL,14,Ffrom carers who described having to
OL,15,F"beg" and "fight" for help.
OL,17,FMany said they had been caring for
OL,18,Fyears without being identified as a
OL,19,Fcarer by professionals despite
OL,20,Frepeated contact with GP surgeries,
OL,21,Fhospitals and local authorities.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@EO]wD@KOUwD@QO]
