CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FMore than 310,000 people in Wales -
OL,7,Fthat is one in 11 - provide unpaid
OL,8,Fcare. As of March 2024, only 4,924 had
OL,9,Fa support plan.
OL,11,FSome carers reported waiting months
OL,12,Ffor an assessment, with no services
OL,13,Favailable at the end of the process
OL,14,Fand said there is a severe shortage of
OL,15,Frespite care opportunities across
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,FThe report is urging the incoming
OL,19,FWelsh Government to act swiftly to
OL,20,Ftransform this situation as a priority.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
