FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,F"Carers are at breaking point. We were
OL,7,Ftold how they must "beg" and "fight"
OL,8,Ffor help, both for the people they
OL,9,Fcare for and for themselves," Peter
OL,10,FFox MS, Chair of the Health and Social
OL,11,FCare Committee said.
OL,13,F"For young carers in particular, the
OL,14,Flack of support is restricting life
OL,15,Fopportunities. They spend their time
OL,16,Fin school constantly worried; they
OL,17,Fmiss out on opportunities and their
OL,18,Fchances of going on to college or
OL,19,Funiversity are severely limited
OL,20,Fbecause there is no one to take on
OL,21,Ftheir caring role.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TOUoD@XO]oD@^OUoD@dO]uD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,F"In 2019, our predecessor committee
OL,7,Fcalled for strong, national focus and
OL,8,Fleadership, and prompt and decisive
OL,9,Faction. Fast forward to 2026 and, from
OL,10,Fthe desperate accounts we heard during
OL,11,Fthis inquiry, little has changed.
OL,13,F"Unpaid carers have shouldered heavy
OL,14,Fburdens for too long, and we must do
OL,15,Ffar better by those at the heart of
OL,16,Four care system. We urge the incoming
OL,17,FWelsh Government to accept these
OL,18,Frecommendations and to act swiftly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
