PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FThe report found that young carers are
OL,7,Fparticularly vulnerable, with many
OL,8,Freporting that they provide care
OL,9,Fequivalent to a full-time job,
OL,10,Falongside juggling schoolwork,
OL,11,Fpersonal responsibilities and their
OL,12,Fown wellbeing.
OL,14,FFfion-Haf Scott was among the young
OL,15,Fcarers giving evidence to the
OL,16,Fcommittee. The 18-year-old from
OL,17,FWrexham cares for her mother who has
OL,18,Fmultiple heath issues including
OL,19,Fdiabetes and mental health conditions.
OL,26,@vD@DswvD@Hsp
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
