OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,F"I think, for me, the main challenge
OL,7,Fright now is looking after myself, and
OL,8,Flearning that you have to keep
OL,9,Fyourself afloat in order to keep
OL,10,Flooking after someone else," she said.
OL,12,F"Now, that's becoming more of a
OL,13,Fchallenge, because I am in sixth form,
OL,14,FI'm working, and I do many other
OL,15,Fthings on the side, and trying to
OL,16,Fmanage those things, and get the best
OL,17,Fout of them, whilst also trying to
OL,18,Flook after someone who can't do that
OL,19,Ffor themselves, I think that, for me,
OL,20,Fis the biggest challenge."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@ZO]
