OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FElektra Thomas is 15 and cares for her
OL,7,Fsiblings. Her brother is non-verbal
OL,8,Fautistic and her sister has epilepsy.
OL,10,FShe told the committee: "When it comes
OL,11,Fto my education, managing how I feel,
OL,12,Fhow my brother and sister are, and
OL,13,Fthen how anything education-wise is,
OL,14,Fis so difficult.
OL,16,F"You want to be great, and you want to
OL,17,Fhave that time to focus on your
OL,18,Fstudies, but you also want to have
OL,19,Fthat time to focus on your siblings
OL,20,Fand you forget about yourself."
OL,26,@rD@YOU
