OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FThe report has made 35 recommendations
OL,7,Fto support unpaid carers in Wales,
OL,8,Fincluding several to address barriers
OL,9,Ffaced by young people.
OL,11,FThese include training for all school
OL,12,Fstaff, a young carers' lead in every
OL,13,Fschool and college, proper enforcement
OL,14,Fof young carers' rights and a
OL,15,Fconsistent delivery and promotion of
OL,16,FYoung Carers ID cards across all local
OL,17,Fauthorities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
