OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,F"Local authorities have their core
OL,7,Ffunding to provide support for carers.
OL,8,FWe are driving a programme of national
OL,9,Fimprovement work and have provided a
OL,10,Ffurther #13 million this year to
OL,11,Fprovide additional advice and
OL,12,Fwellbeing services for carers, short
OL,13,Fbreaks and emergency financial
OL,14,Fassistance. We have also been
OL,15,Fconsulting on a draft national
OL,16,Fstrategy to improve support for unpaid
OL,17,Fcarers."
OL,19,FPolitical parties have responded to
OL,20,FSenedd's Health and Social Care
OL,21,FCommittee's inquiry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@HO]
