OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775127599
OL,3,CUnpaid carers 'pushed to the brink',
OL,4,Cnew report warns
OL,6,FIn a statement a Welsh Labour
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We deeply value
OL,8,Fthe work that carers do. The Welsh
OL,9,FLabour Government published our
OL,10,FStrategy for Unpaid Carers in 2021,
OL,11,Fand so far we've provided over 20,000
OL,12,Fshort breaks via our short breaks fund.
OL,14,F"If re-elected Welsh Labour would
OL,15,Fincrease support for unpaid carers and
OL,16,Fprovide 16,000 short breaks for unpaid
OL,17,Fcarers each year."
OL,26,@oD@TOUvD@AOUyD@RO]
